request.description:
Upload file
- nh dng MULTIPART FORM DATA
    - Key ca trng file l: 'file'
    - Khng cn gi ln tn file (tn file nm trong file gi ln)
- nh dng Json
    - Key: "base64_image" v "filename"
    - "filename" l tn file, phi kt thc bng ".jpg", ".jpeg" hoc ".png"
- Return:
+ NSFW: 0|1
    + 1: Not safe (nh porn/hentai)
    + 0: Safe (nh bnh thng)
